And that is still one of the
bigger challenges, and

00:37:43.740 --> 00:37:46.600
particularly if you're using a
view pager to swipe between

00:37:46.600 --> 00:37:48.680
things which aren't necessarily

00:37:48.680 --> 00:37:49.900
contextually identical.

