as possible as to the

00:39:33.710 --> 00:39:36.826
type of data that you're trying
to listen for so that

00:39:36.826 --> 00:39:39.590
you're not colliding with other
apps which are also

00:39:39.590 --> 00:39:42.160
listening for NFC data.

00:39:42.160 --> 00:39:44.340
There's a couple of really good
